           Operations and Premises Committee
 Chair:  Dr Lewis Griffin (Director of Premises) (l.griffin@cs.ucl.ac.uk) & Prof David Jones (Director of Services) (d.jones@cs.ucl.ac.uk) 
 Secretary:  JJ Giwa (Departmental Administrator - Facilities Management and Operations) j.giwa@cs.ucl.ac.uk
 Minutes Secretary:  Patricia Fenoy (Departmental Office Administrator) p.fenoy@cs.ucl.ac.uk
 Role: This committee provides advice, oversight and coordination of the strategic and operational management of the department’s day-to-day operations, health, safety and security issues, and premises.
 Frequency of Meeting:  Quarterly 
 Membership:
 
          	Director of Services – Chair - David Jones
	Director of Premises – Chair - Lewis Griffin 
	 Dept Administrator (Facilities Management and Operations) - Secretary - JJ Giwa
	Departmental Manager - Jill Saunders
	Departmental Office Administrator - Patricia Fenoy 
	Operations and Premises staff representative - Kyle Jamieson
	Research staff/student representatives - Muhammad Hussain, Malcolm Reynolds and Thomas Stone
	Taught programme student representative - Saqib Kakvi (MSc ISec - 2009/10) 
	Technical Services Group - Denis Timm, Dave Twiselton, David Swapp
	Health & Safety - Dave Twiselton
	 Academic staff - Mark Handley 
	Environmental Responsibility Co-ordinator - Lewis Griffin

 Minutes of meetings:
 Please contact the Committee Secretary for further information.
 
